        <ab>ROBERT MICHAEL BALLANTYNE</ab>
        <ab>THE BOYS STORY-WRITER</ab>
        <ab>BORN AT EDINBURGH APRIL 24 1825</ab>
        <ab>DIED AT ROME FEBRUARY 8 1894</ab>
      </div>
      <div type="inscription" xml:lang="en" decls="#f_S #c_2 #m_IF #t_P">
        <ab>"HIS SERVANTS SHALL SERVE HIM</ab>
        <ab>AND THEY SHALL SEE HIS FACE."</ab>
      </div>
      <div type="inscription" xml:lang="en" decls="#f_E #c_3 #m_IF #t_P">
        <ab>THIS STONE ERECTED</ab>
